		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I really wasn't aware about the technical differences between PAL and NTCS games. So, my answer now is PAL but that may change few days ahead, I'm not sure.
<br />
<br />Developers with existing freeware or opensource games are recommended. That is because their work can be branded and delivered in short time.
<br />
